{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4d2b067b-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20324"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"20324"},"text":"§ 20324.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d2b067c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20324/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter $12,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2023 through 2027.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d2b067d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20324/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Limitation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No funds are authorized to be appropriated for a fiscal year to carry out this subchapter unless the aggregate amount appropriated to carry out title II of the Juvenile Justice and Delinquency Prevention Act of 1974 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5611"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 5611","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002172"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002172"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" for such fiscal year is not less than the aggregate amount appropriated to carry out such title for the preceding fiscal year."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d2b067e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20324/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Prohibition on lobbying","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No funds authorized under this subchapter may be used for lobbying activities in contravention of OMB Circular No. A–122.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id4d2b067f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/647/tII/s219"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–647, title II, § 219","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 218, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/4796"},"text":"104 Stat. 4796","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/322/tIV/s40156/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–322, title IV, § 40156(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-09-13"},"text":"Sept. 13, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/1922"},"text":"108 Stat. 1922","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/386/dB/tIII/s1302/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–386, div. B, title III, § 1302(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1511"},"text":"114 Stat. 1511","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 219 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/162/tI/s112/d/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–162, title I, § 112(d)(1)","children":[],"tail":", (e), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-01-05"},"text":"Jan. 5, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/119/2986"},"text":"119 Stat. 2986","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/4/tI/s106/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–4, title I, § 106(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2013-03-07"},"text":"Mar. 7, 2013","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/127/77"},"text":"127 Stat. 77","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/103/dW/tXIII/s1305"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–103, div. W, title XIII, § 1305","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-03-15"},"text":"Mar. 15, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/928"},"text":"136 Stat. 928","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id4d2b0680-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id4d2b0681-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id4d2b0682-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Juvenile Justice and Delinquency Prevention Act of 1974, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/415"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–415","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-09-07"},"text":"Sept. 7, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1109"},"text":"88 Stat. 1109","children":[],"tail":". Title II of the Act was classified principally to subchapter II (§ 5611 et seq.) of chapter 72 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification as subchapter II (§ 11111 et seq.) of chapter 111 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id4d2b0683-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s13014"},"text":"section 13014 of Title 42","children":[],"tail":", The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id4d2b0684-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/103"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–103","children":[],"tail":" substituted “2023 through 2027” for “2014 through 2018”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2013—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–4","children":[],"tail":" substituted “fiscal years 2014 through 2018” for “fiscal years 2007 through 2011”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/162/s112/e/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–162, § 112(e)(1)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (a) and struck out heading and text of former subsec. (a). Text read as follows: “There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter $12,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2001 through 2005.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/162/s112/e/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–162, § 112(e)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2000—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/386"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–386","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (a) and struck out heading and text of former subsec. (a). Text read as follows: “There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) $6,000,000 for fiscal year 1996;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) $6,000,000 for fiscal year 1997;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) $7,000,000 for fiscal year 1998;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(4) $9,000,000 for fiscal year 1999; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(5) $10,000,000 for fiscal year 2000.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/322"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–322","children":[],"tail":" amended heading and text of subsec. (a) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this chapter—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) $5,000,000 in fiscal year 1991; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) such sums as may be necessary to carry out this subchapter in each of fiscal years 1992, 1993, and 1994.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id4d2b0685-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id4d2b0686-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2022 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/103"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–103","children":[],"tail":" not effective until Oct. 1 of the first fiscal year beginning after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-03-15"},"text":"Mar. 15, 2022","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/103/dW/s4/a"},"text":"section 4(a) of div. W of Pub. L. 117–103","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s6851"},"text":"section 6851 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":", Commerce and Trade."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id4d2b0687-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2013 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–4","children":[],"tail":" not effective until the beginning of the fiscal year following "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2013-03-07"},"text":"Mar. 7, 2013","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/4/s4"},"text":"section 4 of Pub. L. 113–4","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s2261"},"text":"section 2261 of Title 18","children":[],"tail":", Crimes and Criminal Procedure."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id4d2b0688-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Dissemination of Information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/386/dB/tIII/s1302/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–386, div. B, title III, § 1302(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1511"},"text":"114 Stat. 1511","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/106/386/dB/tIII/s1302/d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"“The Attorney General shall—","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"“(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" annually compile and disseminate information (including through electronic publication) about the use of amounts expended and the projects funded under section 218(a) [now 219(a)] of the Victims of Child Abuse Act of 1990 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s13014/a"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 13014(a)","children":[],"tail":") [now "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s20324/a"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 20324(a)","children":[],"tail":"], section 224(a) of the Victims of Child Abuse Act of 1990 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s13024/a"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 13024(a)","children":[],"tail":") [now "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s20334/a"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 20334(a)","children":[],"tail":"], and section 1007(a)(7) [1001(a)(7)] of title I of the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3793/a/7"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 3793(a)(7)","children":[],"tail":") [now "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s10261/a/7"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 10261(a)(7)","children":[],"tail":"], including any evaluations of the projects and information to enable replication and adoption of the strategies identified in the projects; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"“(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" focus dissemination of the information described in paragraph (1) toward community-based programs, including domestic violence and sexual assault programs.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"[For definitions of terms used in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/386/s1302/d/2"},"text":"section 1302(d)(2) of Pub. L. 106–386","children":[],"tail":", set out above, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/386/s1002"},"text":"section 1002 of Pub. L. 106–386","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s10447"},"text":"section 10447 of this title","children":[],"tail":".]"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
